('ART Clinic Barcelona - Diputación 176 (Proyecto ART)', 'Mental Health', 'Second location of ART Clinic Barcelona offering English-speaking therapy services. Part of Proyecto ART - a therapy center specializing in eating disorders, self-esteem, relationships, anxiety, and depression. Team of international therapists providing individual psychotherapy, group therapy, couples counseling, and family therapy with evidence-based treatments.', 'Calle Diputación 176, Bajo', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 623 022 331', 'info@proyectoart.com', 'https://proyectoart.com/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
